      "description": "PlayBox is your privacy-first, all-in-one video player for personal media. Play your own videos, manage playback, and browse movie info—all in one place.\n\nCore Features\n- Local Video Playback: Play your personal videos imported from Files, Photos, iTunes, or via WiFi Transfer. Supports MP4, MKV, AVI, MOV and more common formats.\n- Network Stream Support: Play your own valid HTTP, RTSP, RTMP, MMS, FTP or UDP/RTP streams by entering the URL directly. No pre-provided streams.\n- AI-Powered Recaps: Generate smart summaries, key moment timelines and chapter breakdowns for your personal videos. All processing happens locally on your device.\n- Customizable Playback: Adjust speed (0.25x-4x), enable hardware decoding, set aspect ratio, use background playback, and customize fast-forward intervals.\n- Movie & TV Info Browser: Browse publicly available metadata (synopses, cast, ratings) for movies and shows. This is for informational purposes only, no playback or download is provided.\n- Secure & Private: Protect your videos with optional Face ID/Passcode lock. No user data or video files are collected or uploaded to external servers.\n\nImportant Notes\n- PlayBox does NOT provide, host or distribute any copyrighted content. You must own or have legal rights to all content you play.\n- The network stream feature requires you to provide your own legal and valid URLs.\n- Movie info is sourced from public databases and is for reference only.\n- This app complies with all Apple App Store guidelines and copyright laws.",
